dc_title_s: [Geological Survey of England and Wales : one inch to the mile map. New Series.] Glossop, drift, sheet 86
dc_description_s: Geological Survey of Great Britain. Great Britain. Geological Survey of England and Wales. Sheet 86 drift. Great Britain. Ordnance Survey of England. (Third edition) North Decimal Degree 53.600000. South Decimal Degree 53.4500. East Decimal Degree -1.6167. West Decimal Degree -2.0333.
